snippet: Thierry Henry scored in his first start in a month, and defender Jamison Olave added a goal in the Red Bulls’ victory at D.C. United.
abstract: Soccer star Thierry Henry, back at full strength after knee injury, scores in his first start in a month in New York Red Bulls 2-0 victory at D C United.
lead_paragraph: Thierry Henry scored in his first start in a month, and defender Jamison Olave added a goal in the Red Bulls’ victory at D.C. United.
